Vendored TLS 1.2 Library
========================

This directory contains TLS 1.2 protocol implementation files vendored from
the WordPress Playground project.

Source: https://github.com/WordPress/wordpress-playground
Path:   packages/php-wasm/web/src/lib/tls/
License: GPL-2.0-or-later

Copyright WordPress Foundation and contributors.

Modifications from the original:
- Replaced @php-wasm/util imports (concatUint8Arrays, concatArrayBuffers)
  with local shims in shims.ts
- Replaced @php-wasm/logger import with console.warn shim in shims.ts
- Widened ArrayBuffer type signatures for TypeScript 5.7+ compatibility
- Added vendor-compat.d.ts for SubtleCrypto type compatibility
